description.narrative: The project development objective (PDO) is to support Tanzania's economic growth by providing enhanced transport facilities that are reliable and cost effective, in line with MKUKUTA and the National Transport Policy and Strategy. Following are the key monitoringindicators for the achievement of the PDO: (i) reduction of rush hour travel time of public transport users in Dar es Salaam; (ii) reduced vehicle operating cost on the Korogwe to Same trunk road; and (iii) satisfactory rating of Zanzibar airport facilities by both airlines and passengers.
